~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : ban                                       ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : ban site/user <site or username>

   This command will ban either a site or a user, the names of which are
   written to the files 'siteban' and 'userban' in the 'rnuts/datafiles'
   directory.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : unban, listbans
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

